  "prompt": "What are some good real estate agencies in ahmedabad?",
  "response": "Ahmedabad is a vibrant city with a growing real estate market, and there are several reputable agencies that offer excellent services. Here are some well-known real estate agencies in Ahmedabad:\n\n1. **Nandan Group** - Known for their residential and commercial projects, Nandan Group is one of the top real estate developers in Ahmedabad.\n\n2. **Safal Group** - Specializing in affordable housing, Safal Group has a strong presence in Ahmedabad with several successful projects.\n\n3. **Savvy Infrastructure** - A leading real estate developer, Savvy Infrastructure focuses on creating sustainable and innovative residential and commercial spaces.\n\n4. **Adani Realty** - Part of the Adani Group, this agency is known for its premium residential and commercial properties.\n\n5. **GIFON** - Gujarat Infrastructure Finance Corporation (GIFON) is a government-backed agency that provides real estate financing and development services.\n\n6. **Bagaria Group** - With a legacy of over three decades, Bagaria Group is known for its high-quality residential and commercial projects.\n\n7. **Sarthak Group** - Specializing in luxury and mid-segment residential projects, Sarthak Group is a trusted name in Ahmedabad's real estate market.\n\n8. **Lancor Holdings** - Known for their modern and innovative designs, Lancor Holdings offers a range of residential and commercial properties.\n\n9. **Radhe Development** - A prominent name in Ahmedabad, Radhe Development is known for its affordable and mid-segment housing projects.\n\n10. **Shivalik Group** - With a focus on sustainable development, Shivalik Group offers a variety of residential and commercial projects in Ahmedabad.\n\nWhen choosing a real estate agency, it's important to consider factors such as project location, budget, amenities, and the agency's track record. It's also advisable to read reviews and seek recommendations from friends or family who have had experience with these agencies.",
